divs: Sighting DetailsI was 5 or6 years old and lived on Motor Avenue in Palms, California. I was running about with another boy around my age and I remember the conversation, saying that his dad was in the airforce and he transported some space men in his plane. An additional image in my mind was that they were laying down on racks as if they were shipped. This is all I can remember and just wanted to relay that to you. If there is a person from that location and time period talking about the same thing let me know.
